### Get Astronomy Picture of the Day (APOD) - Today
GET http://localhost:3000/nasa/apod

### Get APOD for Specific Date
GET http://localhost:3000/nasa/apod?date=2024-01-15

### Get All Posts (Default: limit=10, offset=0)
GET http://localhost:3000/nasa/posts

### Get All Posts with Pagination
GET http://localhost:3000/nasa/posts?limit=20&offset=10

### Get Post by Date
GET http://localhost:3000/nasa/posts/2024-01-15
